<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact-Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/global.css">
    <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "/contact-us.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-flex">
        <div class="logo">
            <a href="/">
            <img src="/logo.png" width="300px" alt="Logo">
            </a>
        </div>

        <ul class="navlinks">
            {{#if user}}
                <li><a href="/cars">Our Vehicles</a></li>
                <li><a href="/search">Search a Car</a></li>
                <li><a href="/friends">Friends</a></li>
                <li><a href="/reservations">My Reservations</a></li>
                <li>
                  <a href="/profile">
                        <img src="/images/{{user.profilePicture}}" alt="Profile" width="40px" height="40px" style="border-radius:50%; object-fit: cover;">
                    </a>
                </li>
            {{else}}
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login" >Login</a></li>
            {{/if}}
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
        <h4> NPM Packages Used </h4>
        <p> Express for Routing and Server Logic </p> <br>
        <p> Mongoose for MongoDB Database Management </p> <br>
        <p> Express-Handlebars and HBS for View Templates </p> <br>
        <p> Express-Session for Session Management </p> <br>
        <p> Multer for File Upload (Profile Picture) Management </p>
    </div>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
        <h4> GDAPDEV XX22, Group 4 </h4>
        <p> Ching, Ashton Jude </p> <br>
        <p> Guarin, Raine Louise </p> <br>
        <p> Gutierrez, Michael Luis </p> <br>
        <p> Villamor, Allysa Luise </p> <br>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="footerContainer">
            <p> This is an MCO project for GDAPDEV XX22 by Group 4. </p>
            <a href="/contact-us" class="disable-link"> Contact Us</a>
            <p> | </p>
            <a href="/about" class="disable-link">  About</a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    </div>
</body>
</html>